title: When Insecurity & Jealousy Strain Your Relationships | Sadie Robertson Huff & Demi Tebow
description:
Demi Tebow is so full of light, love, and encouragement. The former Miss Universe joins Sadie to share the heart behind her mission to end the unimaginable child exploitation in the Philippines. Demi and Sadie also drop tons of advice on how to overcome peer pressure (even as an adult!), how to have an everlasting impact, and how to genuinely encourage sisters and friends without giving into comparison and jealousy. Friends, you are not a copy. God created you to be the best version of you. To help Demi bring healing and hope to 80 exploited children, visit: https://www.timtebowfoundation.org

https://liberty.edu/Sadie — Plan your visit to Liberty University today, and get your application fee WAIVED!

https://dwelldifferently.com/  — Use the code SADIE to get $5 off your first month!
